TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: We need to establish a communication base inside the large volcanic crater. The crater is guarded by the core and is inhabited by an alien monster - only the power of our commanders dgun will be strong enough to kill this creature. You should cloak your commander and then distract the creature with a bantha as you dgun it. Once it's dead, build the structures indicated inside the crater to complete the mission. Watch out for solitary core termites on patrol.
